{"tid":1431640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[預左負皮]你地唔好笑葉國謙同葉劉啦","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:11:16.000Z","uid":279167,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ead547dec9169561707e6c57832a37593fb9e43","tid":1431640,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"保皇黨嘅說話<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔係講俾連仔聽，係講俾中間派同保皇黨支持者聽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n然後就好大條道理話成立個獨立調查委員會去揾大台，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">目的係攻擊政敵</span></span>，例如民主派議員、生果報、等等<br />\n<br />\n就算最後揾唔到都無所謂，因為保皇黨已經達到目的，就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">防止中間派流失，以及鞏固保皇黨支持者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定要強調無大台，要文宣配合，要民間記招，大台就係777，做到一個效果係隔空對罵，作為一個政府，同市民隔空對罵係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好樣衰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家政府流失文意就係因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府好樣衰</span></span>"},{"pid":"88f4151538afe2f0eca227408bcb39ccb73a9273","tid":1431640,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"52518d1b52a76c6b22b79eb054e32eb052556ec4","tid":1431640,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"38a53991e2b4d76eb15429b3e008d8081cba551c","tid":1431640,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1f546334688e440ead0aeefae1151144c6399688","tid":1431640,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a7ac3c15bdb960783ef6958550c496dab7bd4708","tid":1431640,"uid":184096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"［港共反攻啦］佢地唔係蠢到以為有大台，佢地係要屈大台<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431630</a>"},{"pid":"6590093df7641d13ad55a20c1bb576a3acaaebda","tid":1431640,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"cbd99ca4809b6f13649a1240e862aa824bf969d4","tid":1431640,"uid":131770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"大台是林鄭"},{"pid":"9481287adc33a9bd4c284969e6caf8499de4ae30","tid":1431640,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"唔通佢會講官逼民反咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b209013959dbe460ed357166875c9223fe93bc2","tid":1431640,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"推，等所有人有意識知道敵方做野係比偽中位/騎牆派同蠢人睇<br />\n<br />\n等同路人懷疑所有對家一言一行"},{"pid":"663bb92c0455bb2fe28c3eba34c82f7c41175653","tid":1431640,"uid":82099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"明<br />\n從612到現在政府都係做比上面睇<br />\n只係將大台指向777<br />\n將佢地收皮<br />\n<br />\n佢地跟本都知自己有問題<br />\n但係問題在冇落台階<br />\n要落就要做曬<br />\n相反有所謂大台<br />\n就會變相又係大台利益成先（好似現正泛民會出現pk野咁）<br />\n<br />\n繼續直指777就離勝利不遠"},{"pid":"de689ae978415788734d6978900c0daff23722d6","tid":1431640,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"為左令廢老廢中支持我地，我宣佈保家衛國文宣行動正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n求幫推<br />\n返工推唔到"},{"pid":"791bdfa4111d169d31be4cb0b39bb1ba22d179f0","tid":1431640,"uid":284590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"可以係一個方向，好過淨係笑鳩佢地戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd89f707075586559b737bc90919eb7d030e2d1a","tid":1431640,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NL2nz5c.jpg\